    <string name="html_info"><![CDATA[
       <h2>Welcome to CardDroid!</h2>
       
       <p>CardDroid is a backport of <a href="http://davdroid.bitfire.at">DAVdroid</a> down to Android 2.3.3.</p>

       <p>This version don\'t support calendar. Only carddav is supported.</p>

       <p><strong>If you have a 4+ device, use <a href="http://davdroid.bitfire.at">DAVdroid</a> instead this fork.</strong></p>       
	      
	   <h2>Usage</h2>
	   Add a CardDroid account in the settings of your phone. Synchronization is handled like other accounts.
	   
